42
00:01:50,350 --> 00:01:53,640
And then in addition, of course, apply what you learn here

43
00:01:53,640 --> 00:01:56,860
to ensure that you're not just following some style guide,

44
00:01:56,860 --> 00:01:59,773
but that you do everything to write clean code.

